name: Deconstruction and derealization | Metaverse series #003
description:
Nature is cyclical, where reality lives in an infinite loop of creation and self-destruction.

Includes both physical and mental processes, transforming our ideas and thoughts over time.

Once we have achieved a certain level of derealization and of not knowing ourselves, it is when we can take a step forward in this infinite process of continuous improvement.

3 continuous processes: the camel, the lion, and the child. Three transformations of the spirit, the Übermensch.
